_sText: Map made in about 5 miniutes, Press detonator shown in screenshot 1, to blow holes in wall shown in screenshot 7. You can also shoot out lights shown in screenshot 4, and it goes pitch black. So i recommend mp_flashlight 1 is on, otherwise you wont find each other. Knives and deagles are weapons allowed, please do test with other weapons and tell me which ones i should include in v2 one. Thank you and enjoy.
